96
00:05:37,710 --> 00:05:38,440
<i>That's right.</i>

97
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:42,940
<i>I'm a pork cutlet bowl 
fatale that enthralls men.</i>

98
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:46,200
<i>First up is a spread eagle into a triple axel.</i>

99
00:05:48,370 --> 00:05:49,240
<i>Great!</i>

100
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:52,330
<i>I'll continue the momentum 
with a quadruple Salchow!</i>

101
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,610
<i>Over-rotation!</i>

102
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:02,500
I was drawn to you because of...

103
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:06,420
The way you skate like your 
body is creating music.

104
00:06:06,420 --> 00:06:07,380
<i>Great, Yuri!</i>

105
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,440
<i>It's perfect!</i>

106
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:12,100
<i>The last jump is a combination,
so it's worth the most points.</i>

107
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,470
<i>A quad into a tripleâ€”</i>

