<i>On to the conclusion for the love-crazed couple...</i>

111
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,200
<i>Er, so how did it go?</i>

112
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:31,870
<i>That's right, the woman casts 
aside the man she seduced</i>

113
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:32,910
<i>and leaves for the next man!</i>

114
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:39,280
That was so cool, Yuri-kun!

115
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,970
That was awesome!

116
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:41,540
<i>Who's that?</i>

117
00:06:42,890 --> 00:06:44,290
<i>I managed to finish somehow.</i>

118
